{"tid":1586612,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Now足球評述員支持年輕人","createTime":"2019-09-22T04:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T04:50:52.000Z","uid":261118,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1be326ac59307e6c185b99b57d7e9b3b153ce9a4","tid":1586612,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T04:50:52.000Z","msg":"梁冠聰：「紅藍」歐聯齊落敗 大戰爭勝要鬥快<br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports-體育】「年輕人對將...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=26712980191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D26712980191&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=404be500\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=26712980191</a><br />\n<br />\nNow 體育 - <a href=\"http://sports.now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com&d=oV4CUVDy1gIsxIQuXHWa%2FdLD3cQOkzCKckuFp%2FmPVdU%3D&h=616eb02f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">sports.now.com</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「年輕人對將來抱擁好大期望，透過每一舉與每一動嘗試改變未來，以行動實事求是，以足跡寫下自己的奮鬥史！」車路士今季受轉會條件限制下起用大量青年球員，他們勇於承擔，背負各個包袱及壓力迎難而上。雖然暫時成績談不上優秀，但至少令「車迷」見到可觀的未來，今周車路士將主場惡鬥榜首利物浦⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}